{"article_id":"9MXr8yALPf9fX6fX","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"As Democrats blasted FBI Director James Comey over his decision","depth":9},{"id":1,"text":"to reopen the bureau ' s investigation into Hillary Clinton ' s private server ,","depth":9},{"id":2,"text":"the White House insisted Monday","depth":9},{"id":3,"text":"that the agency chief was not attempting to sway next week ' s election .","depth":9},{"id":4,"text":"President Obama \" doesn ' t believe","depth":10},{"id":5,"text":"Director Comey is trying to influence the outcome of an election , \"","depth":10},{"id":6,"text":"White House press secretary Josh Earnest said during his daily briefing .","depth":9},{"id":7,"text":"\" He ' s a man of integrity and character and principle , \"","depth":10},{"id":8,"text":"Earnest said of Comey ,","depth":10},{"id":9,"text":"adding","depth":10},{"id":10,"text":"that he would not \" defend or criticize \" Comey ' s actions .","depth":10},{"id":11,"text":"Earnest ' s comments came in response to repeated questions over Obama ' s thoughts about Comey ' s decision","depth":8},{"id":12,"text":"to notify top congressional committees in a letter Friday","depth":9},{"id":13,"text":"that the agency had uncovered a trove of new emails during a separate probe into Anthony Weiner ' s sexting ,","depth":10},{"id":14,"text":"and would , in effect , reopen the investigation into Clinton ' s private email server .","depth":10},{"id":15,"text":"Clinton leads by 3 points in first poll after FBI bombshell","depth":7},{"id":16,"text":"The emails presumably came from Weiner ' s estranged wife , Huma Abedin , a longtime Clinton staffer and ally .","depth":8},{"id":17,"text":"The 40-year-old Abedin \" has complied fully and voluntarily with State Department and law enforcement requests ,","depth":10},{"id":18,"text":"including sitting for hours-long interviews","depth":11},{"id":19,"text":"and providing her work-related and potentially work-related documents , \"","depth":11},{"id":20,"text":"her lawyer said .","depth":9},{"id":21,"text":"President Obama stands next to FBI Director James Comey in a 2013 photo .","depth":7},{"id":22,"text":"White House Press Secretary Josh Earnest said","depth":10},{"id":23,"text":"Obama ' doesn ' t believe","depth":11},{"id":24,"text":"Comey is trying to influence the outcome of an election , '","depth":11},{"id":25,"text":"calling him ' a man of integrity and character and principle. '","depth":9},{"id":26,"text":"( Charles Dharapak/AP )","depth":8},{"id":27,"text":"Abedin hasn ' t been contacted yet by the FBI ,","depth":9},{"id":28,"text":"but will be \" forthcoming and cooperative , \"","depth":9},{"id":29,"text":"the lawyer added .","depth":8},{"id":30,"text":"Comey has come under scathing criticism","depth":5},{"id":31,"text":"since he released the letter , an action","depth":7},{"id":32,"text":"that came just 11 days before the election and reportedly against directives from the Department of Justice ,","depth":7},{"id":33,"text":"upending an already chaotic presidential race .","depth":6},{"id":34,"text":"The Justice Department said later Monday , in a letter to lawmakers ,","depth":6},{"id":35,"text":"that it would \" dedicate all necessary resources \"","depth":7},{"id":36,"text":"to review the new emails in the Clinton case \" as expeditiously","depth":8},{"id":37,"text":"as possible . \"","depth":8},{"id":38,"text":"Earnest , meanwhile , added","depth":6},{"id":39,"text":"that \" we have no knowledge","depth":8},{"id":40,"text":"on why Director Comey \" reopened the probe ,","depth":8},{"id":41,"text":"saying","depth":8},{"id":42,"text":"that the White House \" was not given advance notice \" about the Friday letter .","depth":8},{"id":43,"text":"Earnest said","depth":5},{"id":44,"text":"Comey , a Republican","depth":8},{"id":45,"text":"whom Obama nominated","depth":9},{"id":46,"text":"to lead the FBI in 2013 ,","depth":9},{"id":47,"text":"was \" somebody","depth":8},{"id":48,"text":"who ' s had a distinguished legal career","depth":9},{"id":49,"text":"that was rooted","depth":11},{"id":50,"text":"( in the fact )","depth":11},{"id":51,"text":"that his political views don ' t interfere with his responsibilities as an attorney or a law enforcement officer . \"","depth":10},{"id":52,"text":"Obama \" continues to have confidence in his ability","depth":8},{"id":53,"text":"to do his job , \"","depth":8},{"id":54,"text":"Earnest said .","depth":7},{"id":55,"text":"AG Eric Holder assailed Comey for having written a `` vague '' letter to top congressional committees last Friday , just 11 days before the election and reportedly against directives from the Department of Justice .","depth":3},{"id":56,"text":"( Alaina Denean/AP )","depth":3},{"id":57,"text":"FBI to scour 650K emails for Clinton ties in bulging Weiner probe","depth":3},{"id":58,"text":"In a scathing Op-Ed in The Washington Post","depth":8},{"id":59,"text":"published earlier Monday ,","depth":8},{"id":60,"text":"former Attorney General Eric Holder said","depth":7},{"id":61,"text":"he was \" deeply concerned \" over Comey ' s decision","depth":7},{"id":62,"text":"to send the \" vague \" letter .","depth":7},{"id":63,"text":"\" That decision was incorrect .","depth":7},{"id":64,"text":"It violated long-standing Justice Department policies and tradition , \"","depth":8},{"id":65,"text":"Holder wrote .","depth":8},{"id":66,"text":"\" The department has a practice","depth":9},{"id":67,"text":"of not commenting on ongoing investigations .","depth":9},{"id":68,"text":"Indeed ,","depth":9},{"id":69,"text":"except in exceptional circumstances , the department will not even acknowledge the existence of an investigation . \"","depth":9},{"id":70,"text":"\" The department also has a policy","depth":10},{"id":71,"text":"of not taking unnecessary action close in time to Election Day","depth":11},{"id":72,"text":"that might influence an election ' s outcome , \"","depth":11},{"id":73,"text":"he wrote .","depth":9},{"id":74,"text":"\" These rules have been followed during Republican and Democratic administrations . \"","depth":8},{"id":75,"text":"Holder ,","depth":7},{"id":76,"text":"who called Comey \" a man of integrity and honor , \"","depth":7},{"id":77,"text":"called on him to \" dispel the uncertainty","depth":7},{"id":78,"text":"he has created before Election Day . \"","depth":7},{"id":79,"text":"De Blasio says","depth":8},{"id":80,"text":"Clinton email probe is 'much ado about nothing '","depth":8},{"id":81,"text":"Rep. Steve Cohen","depth":11},{"id":82,"text":"( D-Tenn. )","depth":11},{"id":83,"text":"went a step further Monday ,","depth":10},{"id":84,"text":"and called on Comey to resign .","depth":9},{"id":85,"text":"Clinton herself also weighed in ,","depth":9},{"id":86,"text":"telling a crowd in Kent , Ohio ,","depth":10},{"id":87,"text":"that \" there is no case here . \"","depth":10},{"id":88,"text":"Later Monday , news emerged","depth":8},{"id":89,"text":"that Comey had argued in private","depth":10},{"id":90,"text":"that the agency should not disclose","depth":11},{"id":91,"text":"that Russia had meddled in the U.S. election ,","depth":11},{"id":92,"text":"sparking new concerns about his role in the season ' s politics .","depth":9},{"id":93,"text":"CNBC reported ,","depth":12},{"id":94,"text":"citing sources ,","depth":12},{"id":95,"text":"that Comey felt","depth":11},{"id":96,"text":"it was too close to the election for the FBI to be a part of any disclosure","depth":11},{"id":97,"text":"that Russia had been involved in efforts","depth":12},{"id":98,"text":"to affect the voting .","depth":12},{"id":99,"text":"The report said","depth":10},{"id":100,"text":"\" government insiders are perplexed \" over why Comey would have been concerned about the timing of a statement regarding Russia ' s meddling but not with the timing of his statement about the reopened Clinton probe .","depth":10},{"id":101,"text":"CNN reported","depth":9},{"id":102,"text":"that Comey is standing by his decision","depth":11},{"id":103,"text":"to notify Congress about the new emails ,","depth":11},{"id":104,"text":"and people","depth":12},{"id":105,"text":"who know him","depth":12},{"id":106,"text":"told the Daily News not to expect the lawman to go anywhere .","depth":11},{"id":107,"text":"FBI Director James Comey notified key congressional committees","depth":6},{"id":108,"text":"that he would reopen the case into Hillary Clinton ' s private email sever .","depth":6},{"id":109,"text":"( Cliff Owen/AP )","depth":5},{"id":110,"text":"\" He ' s untouchable , \"","depth":6},{"id":111,"text":"said a retired FBI supervisor","depth":7},{"id":112,"text":"who knows the bureau ' s director .","depth":7},{"id":113,"text":"\" I see him standing strong ,","depth":6},{"id":114,"text":"and he ' ll only resign","depth":7},{"id":115,"text":"if someone tries to force him to do something","depth":8},{"id":116,"text":"he thinks","depth":9},{"id":117,"text":"is wrong . \"","depth":9},{"id":118,"text":"Former agents and federal prosecutors said","depth":6},{"id":119,"text":"they believe","depth":7},{"id":120,"text":"Comey would not have acted","depth":8},{"id":121,"text":"without good reason .","depth":8},{"id":122,"text":"\" He is one of the smartest people","depth":10},{"id":123,"text":"you will find in the Department of Justice , \"","depth":10},{"id":124,"text":"said a former federal prosecutor","depth":10},{"id":125,"text":"who has worked under Comey .","depth":10},{"id":126,"text":"\" He did what he did","depth":10},{"id":127,"text":"to protect the government and himself , \"","depth":10},{"id":128,"text":"the source said ,","depth":9},{"id":129,"text":"dismissing speculation","depth":8},{"id":130,"text":"that Attorney General Loretta Lynch would ask him to resign","depth":9},{"id":131,"text":"over allegedly violating Justice Department guidelines .","depth":9},{"id":132,"text":"\" Loretta is not a political person ,","depth":7},{"id":133,"text":"and I don ' t think","depth":8},{"id":134,"text":"she would execute an order","depth":9},{"id":135,"text":"that is political in nature . \"","depth":9},{"id":136,"text":"An FBI director serves a 10-year term","depth":6},{"id":137,"text":"and can only be dismissed","depth":7},{"id":138,"text":"for committing a crime or serious misconduct .","depth":7},{"id":139,"text":"Obama","depth":11},{"id":140,"text":"- or Clinton or Donald Trump -","depth":11},{"id":141,"text":"could not remove Comey","depth":10},{"id":142,"text":"because they disagree with him ,","depth":9},{"id":143,"text":"but they could make his life miserable .","depth":8},{"id":144,"text":"President Bill Clinton forced out then-FBI Director William Sessions in 1993","depth":8},{"id":145,"text":"after he came under a cloud for ethical violations .","depth":8},{"id":146,"text":"Ronald Kessler , author of \" The Secrets of the FBI , \" said","depth":8},{"id":147,"text":"he thinks","depth":9},{"id":148,"text":"the alleged dispute between Comey and Lynch over the disclosure is fiction .","depth":9},{"id":149,"text":"\" She","depth":12},{"id":150,"text":"( Lynch )","depth":12},{"id":151,"text":"left the email investigation to Comey ,","depth":11},{"id":152,"text":"and he exercised his discretion , \"","depth":10},{"id":153,"text":"Kessler said .","depth":9},{"id":154,"text":"\" It is unprecedented for an FBI director to reveal that kind of information ,","depth":9},{"id":155,"text":"but everything is unprecedented here . \"","depth":9}],"relations":[{"parent":311,"left":212,"right":310,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":212,"left":210,"right":211,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":210,"left":189,"right":209,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":189,"left":185,"right":188,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":185,"left":171,"right":184,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":171,"left":166,"right":170,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":166,"left":159